ErrorDocument 400 http://localhost/400
ErrorDocument 401 http://localhost/401
ErrorDocument 403 http://localhost/403
ErrorDocument 404 http://localhost/404
ErrorDocument 406 http://localhost/406
ErrorDocument 500 http://localhost/500
ErrorDocument 503 http://localhost/503

Options +FollowSymlinks
RewriteEngine on
RewriteCond $1 !^(index\.php)

RewriteRule ^400$ views/error/400.php [nc]
RewriteRule ^401$ views/error/401.php [nc]
RewriteRule ^403$ views/error/403.php [nc]
RewriteRule ^404$ views/error/404.php [nc]
RewriteRule ^406$ views/error/406.php [nc]
RewriteRule ^500$ views/error/500.php [nc]
RewriteRule ^503$ views/error/503.php [nc]